sentences.simplifiedText: 由于他并未完全明白这句话的含义，因此他误解了这一切。
sentences.traditionalText: 由於他並未完全明白這句話的含義，因此他誤解了這一切。
sentences.pinyin: Yóu yú tā bìng wèi wánquán míngbái zhè jù huà de hányì, yīncǐ tā wùjiěle zhè yīqiè.
sentences.translation: Because he didn't fully understand the meaning of the sentence, he misunderstood everything.
